      <title>从哥伦比亚大学到加州大学洛杉矶分校，多所大学尝试停课，并通过对话平息校园抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/columbia-to-ucla-try-suspensions-talks-to-quell-campus-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着学年即将结束，从哥伦比亚大学到加州大学洛杉矶分校，美国各所大学都在忙于应对亲巴勒斯坦示威活动，纪律处分不断升级，校园生活陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/columbia-to-ucla-try-suspensions-talks-to-quell-campus-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 00:30:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上议院称北爱尔兰面临失去兽药的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/northern-ireland-risks-losing-veterinary-medicines-lords-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立法者警告说，由于英国脱欧规定，北爱尔兰将失去三分之一的兽药，这对公共健康构成威胁，并有可能导致英国食品供应链中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/northern-ireland-risks-losing-veterinary-medicines-lords-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国在摩尔多瓦投票前对俄罗斯“混合”袭击发出警报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/uk-sounds-alarm-on-russian-hybrid-attacks-before-moldova-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉英国情报评估的人士透露，俄罗斯计划在摩尔多瓦总统选举和今年晚些时候举行的加入欧盟公投之前对摩尔多瓦发动一波所谓的“混合”攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/uk-sounds-alarm-on-russian-hybrid-attacks-before-moldova-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警察死亡事件震惊智利 寻求加强安全法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/chile-seeks-tighter-security-laws-as-police-deaths-shock-country</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利政府正在呼吁更新安全措施和制定新的反恐法，因为该国正在努力解决周末三名警察被谋杀的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/chile-seeks-tighter-security-laws-as-police-deaths-shock-country</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>学者警告称，中国持有的美国国债正成为“人质”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-s-us-assets-becoming-hostages-divestment-advocate-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家智库发表的一篇论文指出，中国需要进一步减持美国国债，部分原因是为了削弱华盛顿对其亚洲竞争对手的潜在影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-s-us-assets-becoming-hostages-divestment-advocate-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
